data-triple-N3.o: "Preston North End Football Club is a professional football club located in the Deepdale area of the city of Preston, Lancashire, England. They play in League One, the third tier in the English football league system. Originally founded as a cricket club in 1863, the institution adopted rugby union code in 1877. One year later Preston North played its first game under the rules of association football."@en
